==Trivia==
*In the comics, Sharon Carter was originally written as [[Peggy Carter]]'s younger sister, but was later retconned as her niece.
*The Power Broker was the title held by two different individuals in the [[Marvel Comics (publisher)|Marvel Comics]] Universe, specialized in providing superpowers and augmentations for paying customers. The original Power Broker, [[w:c:marvel:Curtiss Jackson (Earth-616)|Curtiss Jackson]] was the founder of [[w:c:marvel:Power Broker, Inc. (Earth-616)|Power Broker, Inc.]] and worked with Dr. [[Karl Malus]] and provided superpowers for [[John Walker]]. He was eventually killed by the [[Punisher]], and replaced by a [[w:c:marvel:Power Broker (Power Broker, Inc.) (Earth-616)|new Power Broker]], who possessed superhuman abilities.

